The main API surface matches the draft, with one important nuance: `UiColor` has public `String`, `Vector4`, and hex constructors that the draft omits, and token alpha operations are resolved through `UiColorManager` rather than by baking a fixed RGBA immediately. I’m checking the implementation details now so the wording stays precise without expanding the guide into an API inventory.
